title: Ultimate 2BR/1BA Condo -  520 Natoma Street 1
posting_body: ['Capture The Charm, Love The Space, Live The Location', 'This updated SoMa flat features 9 foot ceilings and great natural light.', '2 bedrooms, 1 bath, traditional Jr. Suite layout!', '*No Living Room* Kitchen and bathroom have just been remodeled, and unit has new flooring and paint throughout.', 'Stainless steel appliances and gas range in the eat-in kitchen.', 'Plenty of closet space and assigned extra storage.', 'Building features beautiful Edwardian details, common recreation room with wet bar, shared laundry, bike room, and common rear patio.', '98 Walk Score, 100 Transit Score, 97 Bike Score.', 'A rare opportunity.', 'Want to know more?', 'Call today..', '** Tenant pays for electricity, gas, and cable/internet.', '** Tenant(s) will be responsible for following any HOA-mandated “Rules & Responsibilities” and “Covenants, Conditions & Restrictions.”', '**', '** Tenant is responsible for any HOA Move in/Move out fees if applicable**', '** Security Deposit is equal to 1x the monthly rent based upon approved credit.', '(NOTE: In CA, can increase security deposits to 2x rent.', 'Please see the statement of rental criteria here: <URL>', '**', 'If you are interested in applying, please email', 'show contact info', 'or text', 'show contact info', 'to request an application.', 'Please note that applications are reviewed in the order received and application fees are not refundable.', '**']
